<br>
A week ago I was on the west castle wall in PoV. A shaman friend of mine and myself had died due to a golem add. These mobs just do so much damage that even when slowed they can kill the average player in a few rounds. We came back to get our corpses, and a enchanter had move into the camp we had solo. I stayed for about 40mins to watch her, and I was truly amazed. She was charming the golems, chain pulling, mezzing two at a time then debuffing them and let pet have at them. She said she could make about 1aa every 15-20mins. I asked her how often she would die and she said around two times per session but then followed it up to say that it wasn't a big deal because she was lvl 65, and two deaths isn't a issue because there is always a cleric around to rez, and two deaths in level 65 is worth the 5 to 8 aa she makes in less then 2hours of soloing. /boggle<br>
<br>
Yes I am pissed that I can no longer solo with most of the tools I was able to solo with pre-60. Yes I am jealous of the fact that a &quot;group class&quot;, can out damage me whenever they feel like it, and completely, and utterly blows away my solo ability, while being able to get a group with one shout of &quot;lvl 65 enchanter LFG&quot;. That doesn't seem fair or balanced. Enchanters should not be able to out damage three rogues with one spell, and a few buffs when they are not even a damage class. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=absolutemaster>Absolute Master</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 33<br> <font color=#333333>(1/7/03 9:09:53 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm32.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=436.topic&index=17>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://stuwww.kub.nl/~s338419/everquest/gohan.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: MAGE Elemental Silence OVERpowered! Devs Read.</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>it is a discussion, not a nerf class. We comment on it's power and everyone but enchanters seem to agree with the comments. So why take em down when they just discuss the finer points of monopolizing boss mobs.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
